---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Nina from "@/assets/nina-heart.png";
import PinkCloud from "@/assets/pink-cloud.svg";
---

<section id="about" class="my-20 text-zinc-600 body-font scroll-mt-52">
  <div class="container px-5 py-5 sm:py-24 mx-auto">
    <div class="w-full mb-6 lg:mb-20">
      <h1
        class="sm:text-5xl text-2xl tracking-tight font-bold title-font mb-2 text-gray-900"
      >
        About
      </h1>
      <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-accent rounded"></div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="relative flex flex-col space-y-16 lg:flex-row justify-center items-center lg:space-x-32"
    >
      <Image
        width={400}
        height={400}
        src={Nina}
        alt="nina image"
        class="object-cover rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-primary"
      />
      <Image
        width={250}
        src={PinkCloud}
        alt={"star"}
        class="absolute top-[45%] right-[0%] md:right-[12%] md:-top-[3%] z-50"
      />
      <div
        class="relative text-lg text-justify max-w-lg leading-snug text-balance p-8 rounded-md border-2 border-accent"
      >
        <p class="text-zinc-800">
          I’m so glad you’re here, and welcome to a space of healing and
          self-discovery! I’m Nina, the intuitive astrologer behind Honey Nectar
          Astrology. My approach is like drawing out the nectar of your soul’s
          wisdom—using astrology as a therapeutic tool to uncover and heal
          familial traumas and unresolved past life issues. I’m here to guide
          you through life’s challenges with a nurturing, honeyed approach,
          helping you transform pain into purpose and bloom into your most
          authentic, fulfilled self.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
